OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHeavy rain
OL,6,Facross Orkney at first will spread to
OL,7,FShetland through the evening.
OL,8,FOvernight, the rain will become more
OL,9,Fpatchy, though it will remain rather
OL,10,Fcloudy and murky.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FCloudy with patchy rain
OL,13,Fclearing during the morning for
OL,14,FShetland. Otherwise a bright day with
OL,15,Fsunny spells and scattered showers.
OL,16,FStrong winds, occasional gales for
OL,17,FShetland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
